# SignalX AI – Market Intelligence System

## Problem
Retail investors rely on fragmented data and tips, leading to poor decisions.

## Solution
SignalX AI is a multi-agent system that transforms market data into actionable intelligence.

## Architecture
- Data Agent → Fetches stock data
- News Agent → Provides context
- Signal Agent → Detects trends
- Decision Agent (Gemini) → Generates insights

## Features
- Real-time stock analysis
- Risk & opportunity detection
- AI-powered recommendations

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Streamlit
- yfinance
- Google Gemini API

## Impact
- Saves research time
- Improves decision-making
- Helps retail investors
